verbose_text: Ovarian cancer is commonly associated with homologous recombination (HR) deficiency resulting from BRCA1/2 (10-20% of high grade ovarian cancers) and BRCA like mutations (50% of high grade ovarian cancers) XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR, which make them sensitive to agents such as PARP inhibitors that prevent DNA repair XREF_BIBR.
evidence: PARP inhibitors that prevent DNA repair
